                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120115-112-off667 t18120115-112-cd668"></join>, a coat, value 12 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18120115-112-victim1064" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Jones
                  <interp inst="t18120115-112-victim1064" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
